{"tid":1188291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【如一家人】 楊受成有份飲茶兼坐主家席 大姑奶容祖兒送20圍酒","createTime":"2019-06-06T07:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T17:42:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3fcf2c57a5b5c804bbfede144e7a06f5439e43f9","tid":1188291,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:16:54.000Z","msg":"容祖兒被胞弟Samuel爬頭結婚，榮升大姑奶的祖兒送樓又送20圍酒席，昨晚Samuel和空姐老婆Samantha在尖沙嘴的酒店擺酒，英皇老闆楊受成、霍汶希（Mani）、關智斌、楊受成兒子楊政龍等到賀，一對新人還向楊受成斟茶，一手捧紅祖兒的楊受成被安排坐主家席，如一家人般親密。<br />\n昨晚祖兒在社交網貼喜宴相分享，踏入凌晨就是她的農曆39歲生日，祖兒寫道：「原來過咗0000是我農曆牛一，真的好事連連，給我一個願望的話，一定是身體健康。」見證大姑奶誕生的關智斌晒合照，更拍下一對新人拖手許下誓言的畫面，祖兒感謝他趕來飲喜酒：「謝謝關斌收工趕過來，幫手迷倒場內所有美少女。」楊政龍更分享多張相片，踢爆大姑奶祖兒笑到夾住塊面。<br />\n而主持人Naomi（馮鎵瀠）亦有份去飲，更捉實機會向祖兒集郵，留言：「大姑奶...我大佬個家姐」、「大佬娶老婆，做細嘅梗係盛裝出席啦，滾動到喊吖，阿嫂鬼火咁靚，我真係好開心，幸福快樂。甜甜蜜蜜。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190606/large/1559799958_4949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190606%2Flarge%2F1559799958_4949.jpg&h=8e2abc39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190606/large/1559800213_f1fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190606%2Flarge%2F1559800213_f1fb.jpg&h=83e4a665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190606/large/1559799958_9d08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190606%2Flarge%2F1559799958_9d08.jpg&h=9812ad54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190606/large/1559799964_a693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190606%2Flarge%2F1559799964_a693.jpg&h=f09cf16d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190606/large/1559800785_a2d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190606%2Flarge%2F1559800785_a2d2.jpg&h=070c4db3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190606/59683567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59683567&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BguDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=34cbb9a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59683567&h=3d2ac33f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190606/59683567</a>"},{"pid":"585d64bb903c62db49edd0e72b69485ef8cc72ce","tid":1188291,"uid":174601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"親密如一家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264c87a1d2355e825ded5d25d5bf23a1bfe56a4c","tid":1188291,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:30:13.000Z","msg":"結婚都唔修下身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412dc7891da5effb03f104fe807ead2b37f2a8aa","tid":1188291,"uid":27616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"佢食大頭奶粉大？"},{"pid":"25275a67f7cfda4b3d1c35b1d83609eaee17ae2a","tid":1188291,"uid":104218,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rncUVyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrncUVyX.png&h=efdbb9ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3kbXNj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3kbXNj.png&h=2cfd8071&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.